## Zoom - Reports

* Go on to Zoom and Export the same reports you have before for check in to put in the archive and double check the check ins
    -   Zoom > Reports > Usage > change the dates to the workshop > export participants with unique users with meeting data
    -   Zoom > Surveys > Export Survey (Responses) > Top right hand corner there is an download button
        -   rename file with (yyyy-MM-DD Name of workshop Time Instructor)
        
Click on survey <br>

All Results <br>

## Localist – Reports

Before you download, make sure you have checked in everyone who came to the workshop.

Go to workshop  
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl1.png)  
Click on View Confirmed Tickets  
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl2.png)  

Click on Export CSV  
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl3.png)  

A email will be sent to your email account   
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl4.png)  
 
Click on the link  
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl5.png)  

It will download the excel file or CSV 
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl6.png)
You will receive one at a time  
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl7.png)
Put all the files in a BOX folder and share it will the Program Coordinator   
![ ](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CMC-QCL/fellow-handbook/main/Images/Reportsl8.png)
